Package: lightscope
Version: 1.0.2
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, libpcap-dev, python3-venv, systemd, libsystemd-dev, pkg-config
Maintainer: LightScope Team <e@alumni.usc.edu>
Description: Network security monitoring and honeypot system
 LightScope is a comprehensive network security monitoring solution that
 detects unwanted network traffic and provides honeypot capabilities.
 It monitors network interfaces for suspicious activity and reports
 findings to the LightScope cloud platform.
Homepage: https://thelightscope.com
